reviewText: Great video in a style that only Todd could pull off.  He has the ability to break down the techniques and concepts necessary to improve your scores.  You will not be disappointed in this great instructional work.

You will never find anyone like Todd...My scores are moving in the right direction. Two at a time....all the time.
Most of all I just don't miss at 4 anymore...
hubby says that this is a GREAT DVD for tutorial on doubles skeet - Todd Bender is THE MAN when it comes to Skeet - so he trusts every bit of instruction that Todd gives in this instructional DVD.
